== Jianbin Xin

~~~
{}{img_left}{images/Jianbin.jpg}{Temp}{150}
I am an associate professor at the [http://www.zzu.edu.cn/ School of Electrical Engineering], [https://www.zzu.edu.cn/ Zhengzhou University]. I am broadly interested in problems that lie in the intersection of electrical engineering and computer science - in particular high dimensional statistical and algorithmic problems.

